room_title: Escape room "Y2K Mystery" by SUBScape Games in San Diego
room_description: The Y2K Virus is about to knock out every single server in the world, banks are panicking, security is down and NOTHING is in order! There is one coder who may have the anti-virus code to reverse this mess, but he is no where to be found. We know the location of his loft in New York City, its up to you to break into his loft and find that anti-virus!
